          "text": " is designed to handle the processing of meter billing data for a specific period. It involves setting up the meter billing transactions, checking for any missing sequences or discrepancies, and performing a final validation to ensure data integrity. The procedure interacts with other stored procedures and views within the database to achieve its objectives."
